@api_url = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = 
@api_key = your-api-key-change-in-production
@collectionId = 1

### Create Slot
POST {{api_url}}/slots
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

{
  "startAt": "2026-03-15T09:00:00Z",
  "endAt": "2026-03-15T12:00:00Z",
  "collectionId": {{collectionId}}
}

### Get All Slots
GET {{api_url}}/slots
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

### Get Slot by ID
GET {{api_url}}/slots/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

### Update Slot
PUT {{api_url}}/slots/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

{
  "startAt": "2026-03-15T10:00:00Z",
  "endAt": "2026-03-15T13:00:00Z",
  "collectionId": {{collectionId}}
}

### Delete Slot
DELETE {{api_url}}/slots/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
